<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>

    <div class="w-100">
        <div class="w-100" style="height: 60vh; background: linear-gradient(45deg, #d9e98c, #F2F6D0);">
            <div class="container h-100">
                <h1 class="text-center mb-2" style="color: #a91e50">MEAL SUGGESTOR</h1>
                <p class="description">Find your desired meals</p>
                <button class="mt-3"><a href="/searcher" class="link-underline link-underline-opacity-0 text-white">Get Started</a></button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="w-100">
        <div class="w-100 h-auto pb-5" style="background-color: whitesmoke;">
            <div class="container h-100" style="justify-content: start;">
                <h2 class="mt-3" style="color: #5d704b;">How to use?</h2>
                <div class="container border rounded w-75 p-5 mt-3 mb-5 h-auto" style="justify-content: start; max-width: 680px; background-color: white;">
                    <h2 class="mb-4 text-center">MEAL SUGGESTOR MANUAL</h2>
                    <p class="text-center">Get quality meals with your provided ingredients</p>
                    <div class="w-100 ps-3 mb-3" style="border-left: 1px solid black;">
                        <p>Ingredients in search bar should have a comma between them. The resulted meals consist of name, thumbnail and its details ingredients, including missed ingredients.</p>
                        <p>A notification will appear if there are no meals that match the given ingredients.</p>
                    </div> 

                    <form class="form-inline w-50 m-auto mt-3">
                        <div class="input-group">
                            <span class="input-group-text" id="basic-addon1"><i class="bi bi-search"></i></span>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" name="ingredients" placeholder="rice, egg" disabled>
                            <button class="btn btn-outline-success" disabled>Find</button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>

                <div class="container border rounded w-75 p-5 mt-3 h-auto" style="justify-content: start; max-width: 680px; background-color: white;">
                    <h2 class="mb-4">NEED CONSULTATION?</h2>
                    <p class="text-center">Nutritionists are always ready to help.</p>
                    <div class="w-100 ps-3 mb-3" style="border-left: 1px solid black;">
                        <p>Qualified nutritionists can be hired to improve your current diet. Make your dream goal closure with personalized advices and meal plans.</p>
                        <p>Nutritionists undergo a thorough screeing, including testing and interviews before becoming official consultants. This ensures that the delivered programs are professional, effective, and achievable.</p>
                    </div> 

                    <button class="mt-3" style="background-color: #889E73;">Hire Now</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>